p2: mint a portrait based on a single common name
p11: back in the early days of stable diffusion, i crafted this collection of portraits based on a simple concept:
p22: each portrait would be the result of a single common name - with no style or desriptive tags.
p2222: this early ai-art experiment seeks to: a) highlight the inherent biases and prejudaces in AI generated output; b) provide a snapshot of this early stage of AI, with the intention of evolving these portraits as image generation AI evolves.
